    imgQuery:'Caramoan beach rock formations Camarines Sur Philippines',
    reflection:'You are a library. Decades of experience, hard-won wisdom, near-miss disasters, and unexpected grace — all stored inside you. The question is whether you are lending that library to the next generation or keeping it closed. Every conversation with a younger person is an opportunity to transfer something priceless that cannot be Googled. Open your library while you still can.',
