    questions:['Practice 10 minutes of complete stillness today — no phone, no task, just presence with God.'],
    prayer:'God, I receive the gift of slowing down. Teach me to be still enough to know that You are God — and that knowing is enough. Amen.',
    act:'Practice 10 minutes of genuine stillness today — no input, just presence with God.'
