    ref:'Isaiah 43:18-19',
    imgQuery:'Puerto Princesa Underground River cave nature Palawan',
    reflection:'Regret is the most common companion of the second half of life. The choices we cannot change, the words we cannot unsay, the years we cannot reclaim. God does not tell us to pretend the past did not happen — He says do not dwell there. He is doing something new — but you cannot see it while your eyes are locked on what is behind you. Give your regrets to God and look forward.',
