    questions:['Write down your biggest regret and intentionally hand it to God in prayer. Ask Him to redeem it.'],
    prayer:'Lord, I give You my regrets. Do not let them define my remaining years. Show me the new thing You are doing and give me eyes to see it. Amen.',
