    imgQuery:'Pagudpud beach coastline Ilocos Norte Philippines',
    reflection:'Watching a grown child make choices that break your heart is one of the most painful experiences a parent can face. You trained them, prayed over them, modeled faith before them — and they still walked away. Proverbs 22:6 is a principle, not a guarantee. Your faithfulness to the process is your responsibility. The outcome ultimately belongs to God and to your child.',
