    imgQuery:'Subic Bay forest mountain nature Zambales Philippines',
    reflection:'Marriage in the second half of life often looks different from what you expected. The children are grown. The hustle has quieted. What remains is the person you chose, and the question of whether you have truly invested in that relationship or merely survived alongside each other. God joined you together with intention. The later years are an invitation to rediscover, rebuild, and deepen.',
